ystem. That's the benefit of being a big incumbent company: you have other =
advantages you can draw on beyond your product chops.

What is striking about new Siri =E2=80=94 and, I worry, Alexa+ =E2=80=94 is=
 the extent to which they are focused on being compelling products in their=
